Name: Turbo Cat Fight
About the game: Turbo Cat Fight is an Experimental Pixel Perfect Fighting Game. You pick 4 loadouts which total out 20 moves and fight it out with your opponent with your massive arsenals. Challenge your friend to an ultimate showdown of an earthshaking fist trade! Features Pinnacle minimalistic art (watch out for Stendhal Syndrome!) A total of 85 different skills! No deceptive hitboxes, because this game is pixel-perfect! PREVENTS DEATH when you time LifeCling button to your opponent attacks. Best tutorial ever! If I do say so myself.. Music by Visager and Monplaisir, who kindly offered their music free on the internet. Screenshakes?
